<p><strong>SCP-CN-1081：冬来夏往</strong></p>
<p><strong>发布时间：</strong>2020年11月8日</p>
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lyrics-linn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3935168); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3935168&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607560685" alt="Lyrics Linn" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3935168)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lyrics-linn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3935168); return false;">Lyrics Linn</a></span>，进入<a href="/lyricslinn-s-personnel-file">人事档案</a>查看该名作者的更多作品</p>
